{"tid":23163,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"川普副手彭斯：蔡川通話是禮節性 與習近平通話類似","createTime":"2016-12-04T18:45:51.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-05T01:37:35.000Z","uid":35790,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"712745e9ccb34619da6aa89b0e83f7b6807fe8e7","tid":23163,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:45:51.000Z","msg":"川普副手：蔡川通話是禮節性 與習近平通話類似<br />\n<br />\n2016-12-05 00:07<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕總統蔡英文上週五（2日）與美國候任總統川普（Donald Trump）越洋通話，引起國際矚目，中國更大動作抗議，美國候任副總統彭斯（Mike Penc）週日（4日）接受電視訪問時說，這通電話只是一個禮節性通話。<br />\n<br />\n《路透》報導，彭斯在《NBC》節目上被問到川普稱呼蔡英文為台灣總統，相關外交政策是否會有任何轉變，彭斯說，「我不這麼認為」，他說「這通電話是一個禮節性通話，台灣的民選總統打電話祝賀（川普）當選」。<br />\n<br />\n彭斯說，這通電話的性質，就和在11月8日大選後，川普與中國國家主席習近平通話類似。<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1907264\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1907264&d=JQtp7%2BScZlazt5%2F0T0af7GN6obqfy%2FNc7jg2IsrTbnE%3D&h=82f32078\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F1907264&h=fea27e3c\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1907264</a>"},{"pid":"762c73f09916a7c108b2c158f316329766b89fe4","tid":23163,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:49:59.000Z","msg":"愈講愈衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6113b83b89dbaba95f49e12915c9aea1f82ee359","tid":23163,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:50:35.000Z","msg":"把蔡英文跟習近平放同一級<br />\n一中一台"},{"pid":"b7b84a9243688955d6868dd208adf91edbb0d9e8","tid":23163,"uid":29874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T18:57:32.000Z","msg":"我就聽唔到Trump話收唔到English電話，唔通有人特登唔聽屎大大電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0451f06c9fe50eafd8797639d8fa0bc82d458979","tid":23163,"uid":47674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12